# Trivy vulnerability ignore list
# Review periodically — remove entries when the upstream binaries below are
# rebuilt against fixed dependencies (a new HA base image for tempio, a new
# ha-cli release for ha).

# --- /usr/bin/tempio (Home Assistant base image templating binary) ---
# Go stdlib + x/crypto CVEs in /usr/bin/tempio, the templating binary baked into
# the Home Assistant base image (built with Go 1.23.3 / x/crypto 0.26.0).
# Not fixable here — tempio is not an apk package and is not recompiled by this
# add-on; only a new HA base image release can resolve these. Re-scan and prune
# when the base image is bumped. Last verified against base:3.24.1 (2026-07-06).
CVE-2024-45337
CVE-2025-22869
CVE-2025-61726
CVE-2025-61729
CVE-2025-68121
CVE-2026-25679
CVE-2026-32280
CVE-2026-32281
CVE-2026-32283
CVE-2026-33811
CVE-2026-33814
CVE-2026-39820
CVE-2026-39836
CVE-2026-42499
CVE-2026-42504
# Additional tempio x/crypto (ssh/agent/knownhosts) + stdlib crypto/x509 CVEs,
# newly disclosed against the same Go 1.23.3 / x/crypto 0.26.0 build.
CVE-2025-47913
