CVE-2026-46597

# --- /usr/bin/ha (Home Assistant CLI) ---
# golang.org/x/net v0.43.0 CVEs compiled into the ha-cli binary. We already pin
# HA_CLI_VERSION to the latest release (5.2.0); the fix (x/net >= 0.55.0)
# requires an upstream ha-cli rebuild, so this is not fixable by bumping our pin.
# Prune when a newer ha-cli release links x/net >= 0.55.0. Verified against
# ha-cli 5.2.0 (2026-07-06).
CVE-2026-25681
CVE-2026-27136
CVE-2026-39821
CVE-2026-42502
